### 密码模式
POST http://localhost:80/oauth/token?grant_type=password&username=admin&password=123456
Authorization: Basic dGVzdDE6MTIzNDU2

> {%
client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
client.global.set("refresh_token", response.body.refresh_token);
%}

### 自定义模式
POST http://localhost:80/oauth/token?grant_type=sms_code&phone=18511112222&code=1234
Authorization: Basic dGVzdDE6MTIzNDU2

> {%
client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

### authorization_code模式1 浏览器打开
GET http://localhost:80/oauth/authorize?client_id=test1&client_secret=123456&response_type=code

### authorization_code模式2
POST http://localhost:80/oauth/token?grant_type=authorization_code&code=n2SJrr
Authorization: Basic dGVzdDE6MTIzNDU2

> {%
client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
client.global.set("refresh_token", response.body.refresh_token);
%}

### implicit模式 浏览器打开
GET http://localhost:80/oauth/authorize?client_id=test1&client_secret=123456&response_type=token

### refresh_token模式
POST http://localhost:80/oauth/token?grant_type=refresh_token&refresh_token={{refresh_token}}
Authorization: Basic dGVzdDE6MTIzNDU2

### client_credentials模式，没有refresh_token
POST http://localhost:80/oauth/token?grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=test1&client_secret=123456
Authorization: Basic dGVzdDE6MTIzNDU2

> {%
client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}

